00:44:39,890 --> 00:44:41,100
Nakikialam ka na naman?!

728
00:44:46,522 --> 00:44:47,732
<i>Bakit?</i>

729
00:44:49,108 --> 00:44:51,944
Anong pinapakita mo?
Ikaw lang ang anak ko!

730
00:44:51,944 --> 00:44:53,112
Naiintindihan mo ba?!

731
00:44:53,571 --> 00:44:56,115
Sa tingin mo makukuha mo ang mana?

732
00:44:56,145 --> 00:45:01,108
Tanga, mamamatay muna ako
makukuha mo lahat yan!

733
00:45:01,328 --> 00:45:02,747
Naiintindihan mo ba?!

734
00:45:09,086 --> 00:45:09,837
sige ka!

735
00:45:09,837 --> 00:45:10,755
Aayusin ko ang mga bagay dito.

736
00:45:10,755 --> 00:45:12,757
- Mama, pakiusap. hindi kita iiwan.
- Mangyaring, pumunta.

737
00:45:12,757 --> 00:45:15,718
<i>- Mangyaring, pumunta.</i>
<i>- Hindi kita iiwan.</i>

738
00:45:15,718 --> 00:45:16,798
<i>Ayos lang.</i>

739
00:45:43,621 --> 00:45:45,164
Pinatay ng tatay ko ang nanay ko.

740
00:45:46,499 --> 00:45:47,500
Sa kanya lang iyon.

741
00:45:55,549 --> 00:45:56,550
Nanay!

742
00:45:56,575 --> 00:45:58,243
sagutin mo ako please.

743
00:46:03,647 --> 00:46:04,648
Nanay.

744
00:46:08,729 --> 00:46:12,858
Pero, hindi ko nagawang protektahan ang aking ina.

745
00:46:16,111 --> 00:46:18,072
At hindi ko hahayaang mangyari iyon.

746
00:46:18,906 --> 00:46:19,907
Ngunit ngayon,

747
00:46:20,533 --> 00:46:22,159
marami pa akong gagawin.

748
00:46:22,952 --> 00:46:26,288
Hinding hindi ko hahayaang kunin niya ang mga kapatid ko.

749
00:46:38,926 --> 00:46:41,720
Alam mo na
inagaw niya si Keigan kanina.

750
00:46:42,847 --> 00:46:45,683
At hindi ko pa alam
ano ba talaga ang nangyari sa kanya.

751
00:46:46,767 --> 00:46:48,143
At kahit pagkatapos ng lahat ng iyon,

752
00:46:48,143 --> 00:46:49,812
hindi siya naging pareho.

753
00:46:51,385 --> 00:46:52,982
Kasalanan ko lahat.

754
00:46:54,024 --> 00:46:55,776
At ngayon, gusto niya si Keiren?

755
00:46:57,820 --> 00:46:59,530
Hindi ko hahayaang mangyari iyon.

756
00:47:01,073 --> 00:47:02,491
Naiintindihan mo ba?

757
00:47:05,327 --> 00:47:06,829
Hey.

758
00:47:07,246 --> 00:47:08,372
Hindi.

759
00:47:08,372 --> 00:47:09,748
Paumanhin.

760
00:47:09,748 --> 00:47:11,292
Hindi, Jay.

761
00:47:11,876 --> 00:47:13,752
Hindi ko lang mapigilan.

762
00:47:15,629 --> 00:47:17,965
Nakakakilabot ang tatay mo.

763
00:47:19,758 --> 00:47:23,429
Hindi ako makapaniwala kung magkano
pinagdaanan mo, Keifer.

764
00:47:27,349 --> 00:47:28,976
Jay, please stop crying.

765
00:47:29,935 --> 00:47:30,728
Pakiusap?

766
00:47:30,728 --> 00:47:31,937
Napakatapang mo.

767
00:47:33,500 --> 00:47:34,690
Akala ko...

768
00:47:36,942 --> 00:47:38,903
Akala ko masama na ang kwento ng buhay ko.

769
00:47:40,321 --> 00:47:42,239
Mas malala pala sayo.

770
00:47:50,581 --> 00:47:52,166
Paano mo nabawi si Keigan?

771
00:47:53,292 --> 00:47:54,585
hindi ko ginawa.

772
00:47:56,462 --> 00:47:57,922
Pagkalipas ng ilang taon,

773
00:47:58,672 --> 00:47:59,673
bumalik siya.

774
00:48:00,841 --> 00:48:03,344
Kasama ang kanyang bagong asawa.

775
00:48:08,307 --> 00:48:09,975
Doon ako nagkaroon ng sapat.

776
00:48:10,184 --> 00:48:12,019
At pagkatapos, pinilit ko siyang lumabas.

777
00:48:15,230 --> 00:48:16,231
Paano?

778
00:48:17,358 --> 00:48:20,152
Ikaw lang ang nag iisang anak
pinalayas ang sarili nilang ama.

779
00:48:26,408 --> 00:48:27,993
Gabi na, balik na tayo.

780
00:48:31,580 --> 00:48:32,581
Pero Jay...

781
00:48:33,457 --> 00:48:34,917
huwag mo nang ulitin iyon.

782
00:48:36,627 --> 00:48:39,421
Hindi ko hahayaan ang lalaking iyon
hawakan ang mga taong mahal ko.

783
00:48:40,255 --> 00:48:41,256
Kasama ka.

784
00:48:48,514 --> 00:48:50,182
Baka kaya natin-

785
00:48:50,516 --> 00:48:51,892
Hindi.

786
00:49:31,181 --> 00:49:32,349
salamat po.

787
00:49:35,731 --> 00:49:36,732
paalam.

788
00:49:37,060 --> 00:49:39,313
- Magandang gabi.
- Magandang gabi. Mag-ingat ka.

789
00:49:51,201 --> 00:49:52,202
paalam.

790
00:50:11,346 --> 00:50:12,390
ano?

791
00:50:14,016 --> 00:50:15,726
Ano iyon?
saan ka napunta?

792
00:50:22,316 --> 00:50:23,484
So wala kang sasabihin?

793
00:50:24,443 --> 00:50:25,903
Jay, pangalawang beses na yun.

794
00:50:26,403 --> 00:50:27,654
Nakita ko na yung kanina.

795
00:50:28,405 --> 00:50:29,406
Nakita kung ano?

796
00:50:29,406 --> 00:50:30,407
Jay.

797
00:50:33,952 --> 00:50:34,953
Jay-jay, grabe!

798
00:50:34,953 --> 00:50:36,330
Pupunta ka ba
upang pagsamahin ito?

799
00:50:36,999 --> 00:50:38,333
ayos lang ako.

800
00:50:38,540 --> 00:50:40,125
Nakikinig ka rin ba?

801
00:50:41,043 --> 00:50:42,586
Ano ang nangyayari sa pagitan
kayo ni Keifer?

802
00:50:45,058 --> 00:50:46,590
Linawin mo.

803
00:50:47,591 --> 00:50:49,760
Tinutulak mo ba talaga ako
sa aking limitasyon?

804
00:50:50,135 --> 00:50:51,553
Hindi.

805
00:50:51,929 --> 00:50:55,265
Sagutin ang tanong maliban kung
gusto mong sabihin ko kay Angelo.

806
00:51:02,898 --> 00:51:04,316
hindi ko alam.

807
00:51:06,068 --> 00:51:08,946
Wala kaming malinaw na pagkakaintindihan
ng kung ano tayo. Gusto lang namin ang isa't isa.

808
00:51:08,946 --> 00:51:10,864
Tulad ng isa't isa?

809
00:51:11,448 --> 00:51:12,866
Naniwala ka talaga diyan?

810
00:51:16,954 --> 00:51:18,455
Niloloko ka lang niya.

811
00:51:19,998 --> 00:51:21,298
Alam mo, Jay.

812
00:51:21,792 --> 00:51:23,252
Napaka tanga mo.

813
00:51:24,336 --> 00:51:25,796
Magpinsan kami.

814
00:51:26,088 --> 00:51:29,049
Halatang ginagamit ka niya
para makabawi sa akin.

815
00:51:34,346 --> 00:51:35,973
hindi ako naniniwala sayo.

816
00:51:37,266 --> 00:51:38,684
Hindi ka naniniwala sa akin.

817
00:51:39,560 --> 00:51:43,480
Ano ang sinabi niya sa iyo,
"I love you, to infinity and beyond."?

818
00:51:44,523 --> 00:51:45,524
ha?

819
00:51:46,692 --> 00:51:47,484
Iyan ay-

820
00:51:47,484 --> 00:51:49,862
Iyon ang eksaktong mga salita
sabi niya sayo, tama ba ako?

821
00:51:49,862 --> 00:51:51,280
Tama naman ako di ba?

822
00:51:51,280 --> 00:51:52,739
Kaya predictable.

823
00:51:55,325 --> 00:51:57,244
Dahil iyon ang eksaktong mga salita,

824
00:51:57,244 --> 00:51:58,954
na sinabi niya kay Ella.

825
00:53:14,613 --> 00:53:15,030
Hoy!

826
00:53:15,030 --> 00:53:16,323
Masyado kang maganda, ha?

827
00:53:16,323 --> 00:53:18,825
Engaged ka na kay Yuri.
pero may Keifer ka rin?

828
00:53:21,161 --> 00:53:22,162
Ano bang pinagkakaabalahan mo?

829
00:53:22,162 --> 00:53:23,622
gusto kong…

830
00:53:23,622 --> 00:53:25,207
Ayoko nang lokohin si Yuri.

831
00:53:25,207 --> 00:53:26,875
Sorry, Yuri.

832
00:53:27,991 --> 00:53:30,326
Believe me, sinubukan ko talaga.

833
00:53:30,921 --> 00:53:32,339
Pero mas pinili ko pa rin si Keifer.

834
00:53:34,341 --> 00:53:35,342
Keifer...

835
00:53:35,342 --> 00:53:38,762
May sapat pa tayong oras,
para malaman kung paano sila mapipigilan.

836
00:53:39,429 --> 00:53:40,305
Ginang!

837
00:53:40,305 --> 00:53:41,640
Pwede ba akong lumabas?

838
00:53:43,058 --> 00:53:44,268
Ms. Mariano!

839
00:53:44,268 --> 00:53:46,603
Actually ma'am, si Mrs. Watson po.

840
00:53:50,899 --> 00:53:56,405
Jasper Jean Mariano-Watson.

841
00:53:56,405 --> 00:53:57,406
Nililigawan mo ba si Keifer?

842
00:53:57,406 --> 00:53:58,865
- Hindi.
- Paano si Yuri?

843
00:53:58,865 --> 00:54:00,200
Huh... hindi ko under-

844
00:54:00,200 --> 00:54:02,494
Sana hindi ka magsisi
hindi pinipili si Yuri.

845
00:54:02,744 --> 00:54:04,288
Jay, magbihis ka na.

846
00:54:04,288 --> 00:54:05,205
May pupuntahan kami.

847
00:54:06,331 --> 00:54:07,749
Gusto ko ng buong atensyon mo.

848
00:54:07,749 --> 00:54:08,583
Akin lang.

849
00:54:08,583 --> 00:54:09,751
Nakakatawa ka.

850
00:54:12,087 --> 00:54:13,380
Ang panget mo!

